text: René Hooghiemster (born 30 July 1986) is a Dutch cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Continental team . ==Major results== ;2011 : 1st Stage 1 Tour du Loir- et-Cher : 2nd Arno Wallaard Memorial ;2013 : 8th Overall Tour du Loir-et-Cher ;2018 : 5th GP Horsens ==References== ==External links== * Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch male cyclists Category:People from Tytsjerksteradiel
